# 🌍 Societal Simulator — Environment Variables
# Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in your keys.
# The app works WITHOUT any keys using built-in contextual responses + BBC RSS news.

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 🥇 GROQ — Primary AI (FREE forever, fastest, LLaMA 3.3 70B)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 1. Sign up FREE at: https://console.groq.com
# 2. Click API Keys → Create API Key
# 3. Paste below (key starts with gsk_...)
GROQ_API_KEY=

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 🥈 GOOGLE GEMINI — Fallback AI (FREE tier)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Used only if GROQ_API_KEY is not set.
# Get FREE key at: https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
GEMINI_API_KEY=

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 📰 NEWSAPI — Live Headlines (optional, FREE 100 req/day)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Without this key, the app fetches LIVE headlines from BBC World RSS (no key needed!)
# Register FREE at: https://newsapi.org/register
NEWSAPI_KEY=
